          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This optional extension defines a text box for a subtitle sample, to be used as described in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.qtff/documentation/quicktime-file-format/Subtitle_sample_data/Sample_extensions",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". If present, this overrides the default text box in the associated sample description. If the subtitle sample descriptionâ€™s Display flags do not include the Vertical Placement flag (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0x20000000",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": "), the Text Box atom should not be included in any sample of the subtitle track.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
